data.description: Experience the enchanting allure of this three-bedroom, two-bathroom home on an expansive 0.24-acre lot, affording breathtaking views of the mountains. Upon entering, sleek tiles adorn the kitchen, living, dining, and laundry areas, providing durability and style. In contrast, the bedrooms feature dark wood laminate flooring, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The entertainment area is centered around the outdoor landscape with a living room boasting vaulted ceilings with wooden beams, kitchen with granite countertops, a gas range, a large prep sink, and the convenience of a double refrigerator/freezer. The primary bedroom boasts a primary closet and en-suite bath with a double vanity, a generous glass shower, and a Jacuzzi. Additional highlights include a Nest Thermostat, a doorbell camera, an extensive network of security cameras complemented by an alarm system, an epoxy-coated garage floor, and a tankless water heater. Immerse yourself in this Southwestern home's ultimate blend of style and comfort.
